msgstr ""
"Language: English\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"

msgid "loading_screen_tip_1"
msgstr ""
"Finding a clan is a good way to expand your horizons. Browse clans by using "
"the in-game journal or by talking to other players."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_10"
msgstr ""
"You can level spells simply by using them but you can also use scrolls for "
"that."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_11"
msgstr ""
"Collect various essences from fallen creatures, and use them in part to "
"create scrolls you can read to increase your spells."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_12"
msgstr ""
"Quests rewards can be found in your backpack. Task rewards can be found in "
"your bank."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_13"
msgstr ""
"Most monsters are weak against certain damage types, experiment with regular "
"weapons, transmuted weapons, and spells to figure out what works best."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_14"
msgstr "Transmuted weapons are made with the enchanting skill."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_15"
msgstr ""
"Food increases the rate at which you regenerate health and stamina, higher "
"stats yield higher rates."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_16"
msgstr ""
"It is always a good idea to bring food with you and consume it before combat!"

msgid "loading_screen_tip_17"
msgstr ""
"Commonly referred to as “transfers”, stamina to health, mana to stamina, and "
"health to mana are spells used to manage your vitals."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_18"
msgstr ""
"Cast stamina to health, mana to stamina, and health to mana regularly but be "
"careful to avoid incoming attacks."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_19"
msgstr ""
"Your yield while gathering from nodes is largely determined by the danger "
"level of the area you’re in."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_2"
msgstr ""
"Cast Transfer spells like Mana to Stamina to keep your vitals up. Utilize "
"them frequently to maximize your chances of survival."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_20"
msgstr ""
"Gathering in capital areas you get the least resources, in lawful areas you "
"get more, and in lawless areas you get the most."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_21"
msgstr ""
"You can do most crafting in GUI mode by pressing escape and accessing the "
"crafting menu, but crafting at a station may be faster."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_22"
msgstr ""
"All items you loot go directly into any container you have in your "
"paperdoll, if you have no container equipped loot will go directly into your "
"backpack."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_23"
msgstr ""
"Champions are very difficult boss monsters which require an organized party "
"to defeat."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_24"
msgstr ""
"Champions drop rare loot, including some items which cannot be acquired "
"anywhere else."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_25"
msgstr ""
"Access the task menu in GUI mode to find out which tasks you have available."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_26"
msgstr ""
"The equipment reward tier statistic in your paperdoll needs to be a minimum "
"of tier 3 to use the billboard."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_27"
msgstr ""
"Once the village capture score reaches 1200, a player from the winning party "
"will recieve the loot in their backpack!"

msgid "loading_screen_tip_28"
msgstr "Players must be a member of a party to capture a village."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_29"
msgstr ""
"During PVP it is very risky to cast spells when your opponent is within "
"melee range."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_3"
msgstr ""
"If your alignment falls below zero, you will be unable to safely enter NPC "
"cities! Beware!"

msgid "loading_screen_tip_30"
msgstr ""
"Try to fight back with your own melee weapon or block with your shield."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_31"
msgstr ""
"If you want to disengage, you can also use movement spells such as "
"stormblast."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_32"
msgstr ""
"Completing tasks rewards you with items and meditation points, which are "
"used for increasing your stats."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_33"
msgstr ""
"You can also earn cool titles, many of which are very difficult to acquire "
"and come with big rewards."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_4"
msgstr ""
"Drag skills and spells onto your hotbar for easy access! Multiple skills and "
"spells can also be bound on the same slot."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_5"
msgstr ""
"New to the game? Be sure to use the New Players chat channel to ask any "
"questions you may have."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_6"
msgstr ""
"Be sure to talk to NPCs around town and look at the Quest tab, some offer "
"quests that reward potions to raise your stats!"

msgid "loading_screen_tip_7"
msgstr ""
"Buy tools from the merchant, such as a wood axe or sickle, and use them to "
"harvest the various nodes scattered throughout Agon."

msgid "loading_screen_tip_8"
msgstr ""
"Playing solo can be challenging in the world of Agon. Consider using the in-"
"game journal to explore and join a clan!"

msgid "loading_screen_tip_9"
msgstr ""
"Some spells require usage to gain skill in, while others require the usage "
"of scrolls to raise."
